prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?game ?releaseDate WHERE {
  ?game wdt:P178 wd:Q677273 .
  ?game wdt:P577 ?releaseDate .
}
ORDER BY ?releaseDate
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 ?shaqStatement .
  ?shaqStatement pq:P580 ?shaqStart .
  ?shaqStatement pq:P582 ?shaqEnd .
  FILTER ( ?shaqStart <= '2000-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?shaqEnd >= '2000-01-01' ^^ xsd:date ) .
  ?shaqStatement ps:P54 ?team .
  wd:Q25369 p:P54 ?kobeStatement .
  ?kobeStatement pq:P580 ?kobeStart .
  ?kobeStatement pq:P582 ?kobeEnd .
  FILTER ( ?kobeStart <= '2000-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?kobeEnd >= '2000-01-01' ^^ xsd:date ) .
  ?kobeStatement ps:P54 ?team
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?resort ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?resort wdt:P31 wd:Q130003 .
  ?resort wdt:P131 * ?location .
  ?location wdt:P131 * wd:Q142 .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?season ?seasonLabel WHERE {
  ?season wdt:P361 wd:Q5398426 .
  ?season rdfs:label ?seasonLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?seasonLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( ?seasonLabel , "Season" ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q550311 wdt:P800 ?work .
  ?work wdt:P1479 ?description .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?description ) , "middle school" ) )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?composer ?nativeName WHERE {
  wd:Q81534 wdt:P86 ?composer .
  ?composer rdfs:label ?nativeName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?nativeName ) = 'ja' )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK {
  ?place wdt:P625 ?coordinate .
  ?place wdt:P17 wd:Q39 .
  BIND( REPLACE( STR( ?coordinate ) , "Point\\(.* ([0-9.-]+)\\)" , "$1" ) AS ?latitude ) FILTER ( xsd:float ( ?latitude ) > 47.8 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?entrepreneur ?netWorth WHERE {
  ?entrepreneur wdt:P106 wd:Q131524 .
  ?entrepreneur wdt:P2218 ?netWorth .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?netWorth )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q242643 p:P166 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P166 wd:Q194285 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( ?work ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?work wdt:P50 wd:Q30875 .
  ?work wdt:P31 wd:Q47461344 .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q82464 )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?work ?workLabel WHERE {
  ?work wdt:P50 wd:Q312101 .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q11835640 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q47500433 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q83974427 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q110944981 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q110944992 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q110945037 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q110945057 ) .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q110945072 ) .
  FILTER NOT EXISTS {
    ?work wdt:P179 wd:Q11835640
  }
  .
  FILTER NOT EXISTS {
    ?work wdt:P179 ?series .
    ?series wdt:P179 wd:Q11835640
  }
  .
  ?work rdfs:label ?workLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?workLabel ) = 'en' )
}
LIMIT 20

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

  ?album wdt:P175 wd:Q238819 .
  ?album wdt:P577 ?releaseDate
}
ORDER BY ?releaseDate

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?show ?showLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q13979 wdt:P580 ?snlFirstAirDate .
  ?show wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426 ; wdt:P580 ?firstAirDate .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?firstAirDate ) = YEAR( ?snlFirstAirDate ) ) .
  ?show rdfs:label ?showLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?showLabel ) = 'en' )
}
LIMIT 100

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?team ( COUNT( ?championship ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?championship wdt:P31 wd:Q842375 ; wdt:P1346 ?team .
}
GROUP BY ?team
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?film WHERE {
  ?film wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ; wdt:P577 ?year ; wdt:P136 wd:Q20090 .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?year ) = 1978 ) .
  FILTER ( ?film != wd:Q267721 ) .
}

ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q459173 wdt:P2044 ?depth .
  wd:Q513 wdt:P2044 ?height .
  FILTER ( ?depth < - ?height )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

  ?winner wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 .
  ?winner wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  ?spouse wdt:P106 ?occupation .
}

ASK WHERE {

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

  ?winner wdt:P166 wd:Q123737 .

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

  wd:Q1055 p:P6 ?statement .

}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q567 wdt:P569 ?merkelBirthDate .
  wd:Q9545 wdt:P569 ?blairBirthDate .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?merkelBirthDate ) = YEAR( ?blairBirthDate ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK {
  wd:Q1650 wdt:P2043 ?weserLength .
  BIND( 1233 AS ?rhineLength ) .
  FILTER ( ?weserLength > ?rhineLength )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK {
  wd:Q2926117 wdt:P19 ?boulderPlaceOfBirth .
  ?boulderPlaceOfBirth wdt:P131 * ?boulderState .
  ?boulderState wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 .
  wd:Q87192979 wdt:P19 ?broomfieldPlaceOfBirth .
  ?broomfieldPlaceOfBirth wdt:P131 * ?broomfieldState .
  ?broomfieldState wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 .
  FILTER ( ?boulderState = ?broomfieldState )
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?president WHERE {
  wd:Q159 p:P35 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P35 ?president .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate > "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( ?work ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?work wdt:P50 wd:Q7245 .
  ?work wdt:P577 ?publicationDate .
  FILTER ( ?publicationDate >= '1835-01-01T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?publicationDate <= '1910-12-31T23:59:59Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}
